10
00:00:51,160 --> 00:00:53,120
Hey! Kid.

11
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:55,840
How come it's you?

12
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:57,420
Yeah.

13
00:00:57,420 --> 00:00:58,839
How come it's you?

14
00:00:58,840 --> 00:01:01,880
