Hey, Miss.

26
00:01:44,240 --> 00:01:46,239
I don't believe that you have never skipped class before.

27
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:49,639
I never skipped school before, not even being late.

28
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:53,560
This is the first time I've ever been absent from work.

29
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:56,040
Same here.

30
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:59,100
Bye.

31
