40
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:48,840
So...

41
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,959
that's when the picture was taken?

42
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,440
No.

43
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:56,620
