53
00:03:30,540 --> 00:03:35,239
Qiu Bi, bring ten brothers of Heifengtang here.

54
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,680
Heifengtang?

55
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:38,600
What is it?

56
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:41,399
Ms. Jin, are you kidnapped?

57
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:43,180
