67
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:33,199
Of course, I don't.

68
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:37,039
In that case, I had to look tough.

69
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,839
It was a sticker I bought from a grocery store.

70
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:40,740
Five yuan a piece.

71
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:45,659
Well... What happened then?

72
00:04:45,659 --> 00:04:49,660
Then, you bought me ice cream.

73
00:04:49,660 --> 00:04:53,300
