74
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:01,120
I mean it.

75
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:03,599
When I said I'd pay you back, I'll definitely keep my word.

76
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:07,499
I'm a man. A man always keeps his word.

77
00:05:07,499 --> 00:05:12,319
All right, that person and a high school student who's having ice cream.

78
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:16,720
Don't you think having ice cream can make you feel better?

79
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,520
Perhaps.

80
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:39,380
And you said you weren't sneaking pictures of me.

81
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:42,380
But I'm doing it openly.

82
00:05:42,380 --> 00:05:44,460
I'll send you the pictures later.

83
00:05:44,460 --> 00:05:46,440
I'm going to work.

84
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:51,000
What's your name?

85
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,880
My family name is Jin.

86
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:56,279
All right. Miss Jin, my family name is Gu.

87
00:05:56,279 --> 00:05:58,719
Got it. Student Gu.

88
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:03,379
- How can I send the pictures to you?
- Floor 47, Nantian Building.

89
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:14,500
Have the ginger tea first.

90
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:20,920
I thought I had a nail in the back of my head,

91
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:25,320
