94
00:06:34,460 --> 00:06:39,139
It's probable that I found out whom you were at the time, so I planned it carefully...

95
00:06:39,139 --> 00:06:41,599
It doesn't matter what happened in the past.

96
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,380
What really matters...

97
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:49,680
