218
00:15:52,760 --> 00:15:54,340
Right.

219
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:58,800
[Jin Xichen]

220
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:06,940
I'll be there right away.

221
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:15,420
