222
00:16:15,420 --> 00:16:17,040
or...

223
00:16:57,680 --> 00:17:00,980
Bei, maybe I should meet him myself.

224
00:17:00,980 --> 00:17:03,339
- I'm afraid that you...
- I'll go with you.

225
00:17:03,339 --> 00:17:05,840
I believe that I didn't do anything wrong.

226
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:41,219
Run! Xichen.

227
00:17:41,219 --> 00:17:42,660
Run!

228
00:17:45,040 --> 00:17:46,600
You're here.

229
00:17:49,040 --> 00:17:52,900
About our past, I want to talk to you alone.
[JC Group]

230
00:17:59,360 --> 00:18:00,959
I want to be there with you.

231
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:02,319
Don't worry.

232
00:18:02,320 --> 00:18:04,560
