234
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:20,800
[Vice General Manager]

235
00:18:34,840 --> 00:18:38,740
So now, are you ready to tell me the truth?

236
00:18:39,520 --> 00:18:41,759
What's the truth in your mind?

237
00:18:41,760 --> 00:18:43,180
Jin Xichen,

238
00:18:43,800 --> 00:18:47,119
I've been hoping that it was just an accident.

239
00:18:47,119 --> 00:18:49,320
But in this accident,

240
00:18:49,320 --> 00:18:53,880
