241
00:18:53,880 --> 00:18:55,220
Or...

242
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:59,140
are you really the one who saved me?

243
00:19:03,520 --> 00:19:08,480
All these years, I've been thinking about how I should atone for this.

244
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:12,719
How could I persuade myself that I didn't lock you into that van back then?

245
00:19:13,360 --> 00:19:17,420
Maybe the moment when I closed the door,

246
00:19:17,420 --> 00:19:19,840
I buried my conscience at the same time.

247
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:24,340
It was me.

248
00:19:24,340 --> 00:19:28,699
Together with Wu Youyong, we designed to lock you into the refrigerated van,

249
00:19:28,699 --> 00:19:31,800
just to create a chance for me to save you.

250
00:19:32,520 --> 00:19:38,200
Everything was going well until Gu Congbei suddenly appeared.

